{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"654","heading":"Duties of employers and employees","label":"654 Duties of employers and employees","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/ch15","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs654","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":null,"label":"a","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs654%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs654%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall furnish to each of his employees employment and a place of employment which are free from recognized hazards that are causing or are likely to cause death or serious physical harm to his employees;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs654%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall comply with occupational safety and health standards promulgated under this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":null,"label":"b","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s654","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs654%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each employee shall comply with occupational safety and health standards and all rules, regulations, and orders issued pursuant to this chapter which are applicable to his own actions and conduct.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
